==English==
===Etymology===
{{blend|Frankenstein|word}}, Dr Frankenstein being the creator of the monster in [[w:Mary_Shelley|Mary Shelley]]'s novel ''[[w:Frankenstein|Frankenstein, or the Modern Prometheus]]'', the monster being constructed from parts from several bodies

